text: Fuggerschloss Babenhausen The Fuggerschloss Babenhausen is a castle in Babenhausen, Bavaria. It is the home of the Fugger-Babenhausen family, which was promoted to the status of Imperial Princes in 1803. category:Castles in Bavaria category:15th-century architecture Category:Buildings and structures associated with the Fugger family
